data.description: Worried about the skyrocketing mortgage rates?  Purchase this home and you could take advantage of a qualifying assumable loan with a VERY low Interest rate. This Dickerson well-built home is located in one of Summerville's most desirable neighborhoods. A very private yard that backs up to woods. This home comes with $35K plus in upgrades and improvements. Brighton Park is one of the most beautiful well designed and landscaped neighborhoods in Nexton. It has 2 beautiful pools with lots of playgrounds, sidewalks, running trails, a clubhouse with a gym.  Nexton elementary school is in the neighborhood where you can drop off your kids with your golf cart or drive your golf cart to nearby restaurants. Home has privacy fence, lush tropical landscaping in backyard,a patio with Pergola and firepit area for family fun! Ten-foot ceilings give this home a wonderful roomy feel and the Master Bedroom and Living Room are at the back of the house for complete privacy.  The morning sun comes through the Plantation Shutters to give lots of light. Wonderful Kitchen with quartz countertops and a gas range. The gas log fireplace warms the house in the winter. This house is very energy efficient. The Master bedroom has plenty of space with tiled walk-in shower and large spacious  walk in closet with His and Hers drawer systems. The other two bedrooms share a full bath and are roomy with double windows. This home has been well taken care of and is like new! Quick access  to I-26.
